text: John O'Rourke (11 February 1945 - 7 July 2016) was a former professional English footballer. He was a centre forward. During his career, he played for Ipswich Town F.C., Middlesbrough F.C., Coventry City F.C., Luton Town F.C., Queens Park Rangers and A.F.C.
